title: Character Personalities
text:
Evaluation Questions: Do characters of the same GOT houses share similar personality traits? Are there more ‘strong’ female or male characters in GOT? Do ‘strong’ characters hold the most power in Westeros?

tuesdata <- tidytuesdayR::tt_load('2022-08-16')

psych_stats <- tuesdata$psych_stats


characters %>%
  filter(
    uni_id == 'GOT'
  ) -> characters_got

myers_briggs %>%
  filter(
    uni_id == 'GOT'

    uni_id == 'GOT'
